metadata.name: Lama #1
metadata.description: LamaLand is a virtual world of pixel art featuring lamas of all shapes and sizes! Explore the vibrant and varied landscapes of LamaLand, collect rare lama tokens. Experience the unique culture of LamaLand and its friendly inhabitants, and become a part of the ever-growing lama community. From rugged mountain peaks to lush meadows and beyond, LamaLand is a magical world of creativity and exploration.
